*Total Clarity for Partial Deliveries*







Partial deliveries used to leave an information void, creating data
inconsistencies and operational blind spots. We=E2=80=99ve officially bridg=
ed that
gap, ensuring every delivery tells a complete story. You now have the
precision you need to track exactly what=E2=80=99s happening on the ground.
What=E2=80=99s New?




   -

   *Mandatory Reasoning:* Riders can no longer mark an order as "Partial"
   without providing context. Every split delivery now requires a specific
   reason code.
   -

   *Custom Reason Mapping:* Business user can now upload their own
   business-specific terminology. Riders can see custom reasons directly in
   the app.

